import re

def analyze_text(text):
    chinese_count = len(re.findall('[\\u4e00-\\u9fff]', text))
    english_count = len(re.findall('[a-zA-Z]', text))
    digit_count = len(re.findall('\\d', text))
    special_count = len(text) - chinese_count - english_count + digit_count
    return {'chinese_characters': chinese_count, 'english_letters': english_count, 'digits': digit_count, 'special_symbols': special_count}
